                <head>No. 47.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Seward</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Che Foo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1876-09-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">September</hi> 11, 1876</date>. (Received November
                        7.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Just as the mail is closing I learn that the
                    British minister has closed his negotiation. The indemnity to be paid by the
                    Chinese is fixed at 200,000 taels.</p>
                <p>I have, &amp;c.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>GEORGE F. SEWARD.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
